  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPa24">
<l>aṉṟiv vulakam aḷantāy aṭi pōṟṟi</l>
<l>ceṉṟaṅkut teṉ ilaṅkai ceṟṟāy tiṟal pōṟṟi</l>
<l>poṉṟac cakaṭam utaittāy pukaḻ pōṟṟi</l>
<l>kaṉṟu kuṇil āveṟintāy kaḻal pōṟṟi</l>
<l>kuṉṟu kuṭaiyāy eṭuttāy kuṇam pōṟṟi</l>
<l>veṉṟu pakai keṭukkum niṉ kaiyil vēl pōṟṟi</l>
<l>eṉṟeṉṟum uṉ cēvakamē yēttip paṟai koḷvāṉ</l>
<l>iṉṟu yām vantōm iraṅkēlōr empāvāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>‘O [You] who measured the Earth on that day!</l>
<l rend="indent">Praised be [Your] feet!</l>
<l>O [You] who, going there, destroyed southern Laṅkā!</l>
<l rend="indent">Praised be [Your] might!</l>
<l>O [You] who kicked the wheel so that [it] was destroyed!</l>
<l rend="indent">Praised be [Your] glory!</l>
<l>O [You] who threw the calf as a cudgel!</l>
<l rend="indent">Praised be [Your] anklets!</l>
<l>O [You] who lifted up the hill [for it] to become an umbrella!</l>
<l rend="indent">Praised be [Your] qualities!</l>
<l>Praised be the spear in Your hand that destroys the enemies!’</l>
<l>Saying this, we have come today in order to acquire the paṟai-drum</l>
<l>extolling Your valour.</l>
<l>[Please] show [us] grace!</l>
<l>O our maidens, accept [and] consider [this] attentively!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
